## Python Environment

All scripts use the project-local virtual environment at `.venv/`. Dependencies are already installed.

**Always invoke Python as:**
```
.venv/bin/python workspace_init.py
.venv/bin/python scripts/jira_requirements.py create
.venv/bin/python scripts/suite_generator.py
.venv/bin/python scripts/case_generator.py
```

Never use bare `python`, `python3`, or run `pip install`. Never use a system interpreter.

